des:
Motherland FM NG is an Online broadcasting Radio Station established in January 2021 located in Essex UK.
At Motherland FM NG we believe life is all about living for others and serving humanity that is why “ nothing is higher than rendering Service to Humanity” Serving and supporting humanity by doing a small act of kindness is what gives us inner joy, happiness, and satisfaction.

At Motherland FM NG we broadcast live talk shows. music, current affairs, and all that can make the world a better place for us all.
